Description:
    This will generate the boilerplate model, controller, route, spec & serializer for equipment model.
    Remember to add associations.

Example:
    rails generate equipment Modem ports:references speed:string

    This will create:
        Model:      app/models/modem.rb
        Controller: app/controllers/api/v1/modems_controller.rb
        Serializer: app/serializers/modem_serializer.rb
        Spec:       spec/controllers/api/v1/modems_controller_spec.rb
        Factory:    spec/factories/modems.yml
        Migration:  db/migrate/XXX_create_modems.rb


